+1 Veteran level for all military ground units built in your cities (cumulative to Barracks only in the continent where it is built).
-=- "King Richard's Crusade" 300. Obsolete by Flight:
+50% chance of veteran after a battle, for all military ground units. Increases by 24 the Empire Size base limit (prevents 1 or 2 unhappy citizens per city). 
